%%{init: {
  "theme": "base",
  "themeVariables": {
    "actorBkg": "#ffffff",
    "actorBorder": "#a98de6",
    "actorTextColor": "#2f3152",
    "signalColor": "#3f425d",
    "signalTextColor": "#2f3152",
    "labelBoxBkgColor": "#fff4b8",
    "labelBoxBorderColor": "#f1c84c",
    "labelTextColor": "#2f3152",
    "noteBkgColor": "#fffdf1",
    "noteBorderColor": "#d3d7f0",
    "sequenceNumberColor": "#2f3152",
    "fontFamily": "Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"
  }
}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Administrator
    participant Reporting as "Reporting Service"
    participant FHIR as "FHIR Mapper"
    participant Connector as "DHIS2 Connector"
    participant DHIS2 as "DHIS2 Platform (External)"
    participant CentralDB as "Central Database"

    Note over Administrator,CentralDB: FR18-FR21: Reporting and Interoperability
    Administrator->>Reporting: Generate monthly coverage report
    Reporting->>CentralDB: Query aggregated stats
    CentralDB-->>Reporting: Raw data
    Reporting->>Reporting: Generate PDF/CSV
    Reporting-->>Administrator: Download file

    Note over Reporting,CentralDB: Scheduled sync process
    Reporting->>Connector: Trigger weekly sync
    Connector->>CentralDB: Fetch unsynced records
    CentralDB-->>Connector: List of patients / immunizations
    loop For each record
      Connector->>FHIR: Map to FHIR resources
      FHIR->>FHIR: Map patient -> FHIR Patient
      FHIR->>FHIR: Map dose -> FHIR Immunization
      FHIR-->>Connector: Return FHIR bundle
      Connector->>DHIS2: POST /api/tracker (auth)
      alt Sync success
        DHIS2-->>Connector: 200 OK (import summary)
        Connector->>CentralDB: Update sync timestamp
      else Validation error
        DHIS2-->>Connector: 409 Conflict
        Connector->>CentralDB: Log error
      end
    end
    Connector-->>Reporting: Sync complete
